description: At Captain Zion Nicholas' precinct, things run a little differently. Sure, Zion and his officers are sworn to protect the citizenry and uphold the law, and they take their job seriously, but it's kind of a quiet town so there's no end to the down time, and the Captain and his officers do what they can to fill the idle hours. Officer Princeton Price is maybe the most creative at 'filling' his time, which is why he's the Captain's favorite. Or maybe it's because he sucks Zion off behind closed doors, and lets him bend him over the desk and fuck the cum out of him before getting drenched by a Captain cum shower. Or it could be because he's really good at filing...Enjoy!
title: Deep Undercover
